# Android Emulator Docker Environment

This repository provides a Docker environment for setting up and running Android emulators. It enables configuring emulators with specific device models and settings, with automation scripts for starting and managing emulators.

## Table of Contents

- [Overview](#overview)
- [Requirements](#requirements)
- [Docker Image Details](#docker-image-details)
